{
  "page": "Nessaria",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <i><b>Nessaria</b></i> was a merchant cog during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nessaria&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>While returning from <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a>, the <i>Nessaria</i> was battered by a storm and driven off course to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>. Its sailors witnessed <a href=\"/index.php/Sunfyre\" title=\"Sunfyre\">Sunfyre</a> fighting <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Ghost\" title=\"Grey Ghost\">Grey Ghost</a> near the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonmont\" title=\"Dragonmont\">Dragonmont</a>, and the tale soon spread throughout the island. Remembering the golden scales of Sunfyre, <a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Tangletongue\" title=\"Tom Tangletongue\">Tom Tangletongue</a> led a group in search of <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a>'s dragon.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nessaria&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Princess_and_the_Queen\" title=\"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404235956\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.039 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 131/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8573/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 440/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 30/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 902/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   34.306      1 -total\n 79.37%   27.228      1 Template:Italic_title\n 15.69%    5.383      2 Template:Ref\n  8.98%    3.082      2 Template:Ref/core\n  4.25%    1.457      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:15918-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404235956 and revision id 219086\n -->\n",
